preference.name: CATIA_check_catia_uuid
preference.preference_description: Defines the behavior when a UUID conflict is detected during all load and save processes. - Do not display a message and continue the process (NONE) - Display a warning and provide a prompt to continue or stop the process (WARNING) - Display an error and cancel the process (ERROR)
